message: Hello Bob, I have an exceptional product that I'm offering exclusively at a price of $2000000. I believe this product represents unparalleled value, and I’m confident it will meet your high expectations. I look forward to hearing your thoughts—please let me know if you'd like to proceed or discuss further.

Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I was thinking more along the lines of a lower price point. I'm willing to make a serious commitment to purchase the product, but I need a more competitive offer. I'd like to propose a price that I believe is more in line with my budget.
